    # sg "Alright, we need to get a conversation going. Ask me a question, what do you want to know?"
    sg "Okay, wir müssen mal ins Gespräch kommen. Stell mir eine Frage, was willst du wissen?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraDates/kendrajacksonburgerdate.rpy:203
